Author: Serg_V
Title: [ANN] SubSoil Blockchain Investitions
Body: Good day to all who are involved in our branch and is monitoring our progress and the progress of the project. Today we publish the promised report on the next trip to our fields. The research expedition was successful, the results fully meet our expectations.  Video report from our working group, You can see on our channel.  Link to video playlist from last expedition: Expedition for samples. July 2018  In the report, you will see how to clean the rock under the guidance of our geologist, search and separation of samples. In a walk through the field, you can see the real appearance of the granite massif, and even the surface occurrence.  General view of the rock yield at the field.  https://c.radikal.ru/c24/1807/bb/6c0c6eaf1d9a.jpg    Extracted samples.  https://d.radikal.ru/d40/1807/5e/56de18958e97.jpg    granite Quality “on the face”.  https://b.radikal.ru/b35/1807/83/6785fe409a12.jpg    we are ready to “stab”. Outputs of the breed everywhere.  https://b.radikal.ru/b05/1807/e5/249f8ea9ee63.jpg     you can easily estimate the amount of stone visually.  https://b.radikal.ru/b04/1807/b0/b6610ec23302.jpg     on the Left, the sample from Drugoretskoe (Russian Federation, Kareliya), on the right is our “investment”.  please note our stone is blacker than. So its quality is better, and, consequently, the final price of raw materials will be higher.  https://d.radikal.ru/d20/1807/28/1d88efb4a866.jpg    The approximate price of cubic meter of our stone is 35-40 thousand rubles, with an average profitability of such a career of 30 million rubles per month, against 25-40 thousand rubles of the extracted stone in the already working fields of Karelia, bringing income to their owners about 15 million per month, with the current volume of production and demand in the market. But the existing deposits are very close to closure, raw material reserves are running out, and the demand for stone is growing, and the price is growing. Thus, our deposits should reach the leading positions in the future. We will process the extracted samples for texture disclosure and quality evaluation by investors.  At the moment we are actively developing a new WhitePaper. The result will be this week (we will announce the ICO terms later). As well as the preparation of the first “off-chain” sale of one of the fields. We'll have our first major investor.  We remind you that we have an experienced team with many years of successful work on the territory of Karelia (all information about us is available), we have received all the necessary documents for these fields (there is in the header of the topic).  Write to us and we will send any information you need within the project. Do not miss your chance of a great investment, earn with us!

Author: Serg_V
Title: [ANN] SubSoil Blockchain Investitions
Body: A regular field visit was held to implement the program for the search and evaluation of deposits of block stone in the Suojärvi district of the Republic of Karelia. Based on the results of the trip, samples of stone were taken for study, confirmation of predicted resources was received at the declared subsoil area, one of the areas for detailed exploration within the project program was identified.  According to plans, there will be another exit for the purpose of reconnaissance of the sites declared in the list for granting licenses, as well as for the purpose of determining the site for the second possible anchor investor. In total, we plan to attract up to two anchor investors for maximum and candidates are already available. Areas are roughly defined.  Visits to investors will be made during the period from 16 to 25 August.  We present you a small photo report of the work performed:    Moving to the field.  http://b.radikal.ru/b22/1808/8d/08ae7619b5f3.jpg    Survey.  http://b.radikal.ru/b27/1808/b2/c71c3512d81b.jpg    Our geologist at work.  http://c.radikal.ru/c11/1808/2e/a999625f69d2.jpg    The collected samples are numbered and accounted for.  http://b.radikal.ru/b29/1808/75/eb0cdd63cf1a.jpg

Author: kpozdnikin
Title: [ANN] SubSoil Blockchain Investitions
Body: On August 21, a presentation of one of the sites prepared for anchor investors was held. An introductory meeting was held with applicants for investing in the project (by the owners of a large stone processing enterprise) and leaving for Helga.  They showed the materials of past surveys, the results of previous work, held negotiations on the volume of investments. Despite the heavy rain, investors spent quite a long time on the site, examined the outcrops of the gabro-diabase, took samples of the rock, surveyed the infrastructure (roads, power networks and railways) and places of future location of industrial quarry facilities.  The result of the trip is positive, it was decided to continue the negotiations, a more detailed survey of the proposed site by investors. The stone and its volumes were liked by investors.  Photo from this trip u can see in our instagram page https://www.instagram.com/p/BmxsFG5HqMF/?taken-by=sbinvestitions

Author: kpozdnikin
Title: [ANN] SubSoil Blockchain Investitions
Body: Hi!)) No, we are a design and engineering company, we specialize in the search and design of objects for the extraction and mining of minerals, specifically black granite.  We have been working in Karelia for more than 13 years now.  Previously, we worked with local, Russian investors, but now it has become much more difficult, since no one wants to invest and wait for 2-3 years, everyone wants to buy an already ready deposit - this is due to changes in the market.  And so, we decided to try to collect the funds necessary for the development of our new products abroad.  After we prepare the documents for our deposits, we will sell them on the local market to large mining companies that are already interested in our new facilities.

Author: kpozdnikin
Title: [ANN] SubSoil Blockchain Investitions
Body: We have already sold several such deposits, but we did it on order, and most of the profits went to our investors. But we also earned decently. This is our business, we are the custodians of engineering secrets, connections, many years of experience in developing and approving documentation in Russia, obtaining licenses.  You can check our details, our partners, our past projects. We are absolutely honest and open company, judge us strictly!  Welcome to our instagram account https://www.instagram.com/sbinvestitions/. All news will be there before we made our own news page in sbinvest.pro
